      "width": 320,
      "height": 245,
      "text": "name: CI/CD Pipeline\non:\n  push:\n    branches: [main]\njobs:\n  lint:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    steps:\n      - uses: actions/checkout@v4\n      - run: npm run lint\n  unit-tests:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    steps:\n      - run: npm test\n  build:\n    needs: [lint, unit-tests,\n            integration, security]\n    steps:\n      - run: docker build -t app .\n      - run: docker push app:$SHA",
      "originalText": "name: CI/CD Pipeline\non:\n  push:\n    branches: [main]\njobs:\n  lint:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    steps:\n      - uses: actions/checkout@v4\n      - run: npm run lint\n  unit-tests:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    steps:\n      - run: npm test\n  build:\n    needs: [lint, unit-tests,\n            integration, security]\n    steps:\n      - run: docker build -t app .\n      - run: docker push app:$SHA",
