    {
      "id": "rollback-procedure-code",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 770,
      "y": 448,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 245,
      "text": "# Automated rollback steps:\n\n1. Detect failure via health check\n   curl -f https://app.prod/health\n\n2. Revert to previous Docker tag\n   kubectl rollout undo \\\n     deployment/app -n production\n\n3. Verify rollback succeeded\n   kubectl rollout status \\\n     deployment/app -n production\n\n4. Notify team via Slack\n   POST /api/chat.postMessage\n   \"Rollback complete: v1.2.3\n    -> v1.2.2\"\n\n5. Create incident ticket\n   gh issue create --label bug",
      "originalText": "# Automated rollback steps:\n\n1. Detect failure via health check\n   curl -f https://app.prod/health\n\n2. Revert to previous Docker tag\n   kubectl rollout undo \\\n     deployment/app -n production\n\n3. Verify rollback succeeded\n   kubectl rollout status \\\n     deployment/app -n production\n\n4. Notify team via Slack\n   POST /api/chat.postMessage\n   \"Rollback complete: v1.2.3\n    -> v1.2.2\"\n\n5. Create incident ticket\n   gh issue create --label bug",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "strokeColor": "#22c55e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
